0social%20media%20platform%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20has%20faced%20significant%20criticism%20for%20its%20quality%20and%20safety%20practices%20following%20two%20incidents%20in%20January%20this%20year.%20In%20the%20first%2C%20the%20door%20plug%20of%20a%20Boeing%20737%20Max%20blew%20off%20mid-flight%2C%20leaving%20a%20large%20hole%20in%20the%20side%20of%20an%20Alaska%20Airlines%20plane.%20In%20the%20same%20month%2C%20another%20Boeing%20aircraft%20had%20its%20nose%20wheel%20fall%20off%20just%20before%20a%20Delta%20flight%20took%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20company%20has%20been%20explicitly%20targeted%20on%20social%20media%20by%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20other%20traditional%20critics%2C%20who%20suggest%20that%20some%20of%20Boeing's%20quality%20issues%20stem%20from%20its%20decision%20to%20include%20diversity%20targets%20in%20its%202022%20bonus%20plan.%20After%20facing%20these%20criticisms%2C%20Boeing%20revised%20its%20incentive%20plan%20to%20focus%20more%20on%20quality%20and%20safety%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20concept%20of%20DEI%20%E2%80%94%20which%20encompasses%20women%2C%20people%20of%20colour%2C%20and%20those%20in%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%20%E2%80%94%20has%20come%20under%20attack%20in%20the%20US.%20Detractors%20argue%20openly%20that%20DEI%20employees%20lack%20the%20qualifications%2C%20skills%2C%20or%20intelligence%20to%20contribute%20to%20society%20through%20jobs%2C%20education%2C%20or%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20also%20consider%20whether%20the%20anti-DEI%20sentiment%20has%20had%20any%20impact%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EResentment%20In%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Alaska%20Airlines%20incident%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20posted%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BDo%20you%20want%20to%20fly%20in%20an%20airplane%20where%20they%20prioritised%20DEI%20hiring%20over%20your%20safety%3F%20That%20is%20actually%20happening.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20later%3A%20%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20die%20due%20to%20DEI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20indicate%20that%20investigations%20into%20the%20incidents%20pointed%20to%20other%20factors%2C%20including%20a%20lack%20of%20quality%20control%2C%20outdated%20technology%2C%20and%20financial%20irregularities.%20However%2C%20these%20findings%20did%20not%20satisfy%20DEI%20critics%2C%20who%20celebrated%20Boeing's%20November%201%20announcement%20of%20dismantling%20its%20DEI%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20step%20may%20seem%20exaggerated%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20anti-DEI%20movement%20in%20the%20US.%20Another%20American%20billionaire%2C%20Bill%20Ackman%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%20that%20DEI%20policies%20were%20%26quot%3Binherently%20racist%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Billegal%26quot%3B%2C%20despite%20claims%20that%20they%20work%20%26quot%3Bon%20behalf%20of%20the%20oppressed%26quot%3B.%20Musk%20endorsed%20these%20views%2C%20even%20as%20his%20company%20Tesla%20reportedly%20removed%20all%20outreach%20programmes%20for%20minority%20communities%20from%20its%20annual%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20pushback%20against%20DEI%20programmes%20has%20led%20companies%20like%20Toyota%2C%20Ford%2C%20and%20others%20to%20re-evaluate%20or%20even%20close%20down%20their%20DEI%20departments.%20Experts%20attribute%20this%20backlash%20to%20social%20tension%2C%20largely%20coming%20from%20%E2%80%98white%20Americans'%20who%20feel%20disadvantaged%20in%20the%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Indian%20Scenario%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20DEI%20was%20an%20alien%20concept%20until%20multinational%20companies%20(MNCs)%20introduced%20it%2C%20mostly%20due%20to%20mandates%20from%20their%20foreign%20parent%20companies.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20IT%20and%20services%20sectors%20have%20implemented%20formal%20DEI%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20DEI%20initiatives%20tend%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20inclusion%20of%20women%2C%20queer%20people%2C%20and%2C%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20those%20with%20physical%20disabilities.%20Given%20that%20the%20policy%20is%20largely%20US-inspired%2C%20are%20Indian%20companies%20facing%20similar%20challenges%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDEI%20expert%20Saundarya%20Rajesh%2C%20founder-president%20of%20the%20Avtar%20Group%2C%20states%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20some%20global%20organisations%20are%20choosing%20to%20dismantle%20DEI.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20phenomenon%20that%20has%20severe%20local%20implications%20in%20India%20Inc.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCorporate%20India%20continues%20to%20recognise%20that%20inclusion%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20organisational%20culture%20and%20a%20non-negotiable%20employee%20experience%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20delivered.%E2%80%9D%20Indian%20subsidiaries%20of%20MNCs%20and%20some%20prominent%20Indian%20conglomerates%20have%20set%20diversity%20hiring%20as%20a%20goal.%20This%20is%20often%20driven%20by%20investor%20pressure%20or%20requirements%20from%20global%20partners%2C%20and%20the%20easiest%20way%20to%20meet%20these%20demands%20is%20by%20reserving%20roles%20for%20women%20in%20HR%2C%20ESG%2C%20finance%2C%20digital%2C%20communications%2C%20and%20other%20areas%2C%20as%20talent%20in%20these%20functions%20is%20readily%20available%20in%20the%20local%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20roles%20in%20infrastructure%20and%20other%20front-facing%20sectors%20rarely%20see%20diversity%20hiring%2C%20as%20companies%20do%20not%20specifically%20reserve%20positions%20for%20women%20in%20these%20areas.%20Though%20diversity%20in%20such%20roles%20is%20often%20selected%20on%20merit%2C%20some%20companies%20aim%20to%20prioritise%20diversity%20in%20hiring%2C%20which%20can%20inadvertently%20exclude%20male%20candidates.%20This%20leads%20to%20discontent%20among%20those%20who%20feel%20overlooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPositive%20discrimination%20must%20always%20ensure%20that%20merit%20is%20never%20compromised.%20If%20we%20can%20uphold%20this%20principle%2C%20much%20of%20the%20political%20hijacking%20associated%20with%20DEI%20can%20be%20addressed.%20You%20may%20still%20select%20a%20DEI%20nominee%2C%20but%20only%20if%20they%20are%20on%20par%20with%20the%20rest.%20Not%20one%20bit%20less%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prabir%20Jha%2C%20founder%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%20of%20Prabir%20Jha%20People%20Advisory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoss%20of%20Talent%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDEI%20policies%20were%20originally%20designed%20to%20foster%20inclusivity%20by%20ensuring%20diverse%20representation%20in%20workplaces.%20However%2C%20their%20implementation%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20compromising%20meritocracy%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20US.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20potential%20talent%20and%20opportunity%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFocusing%20on%20DEI%20does%20not%20necessitate%20a%20compromise%20on%20meritocracy.%20What%20it%20requires%20is%20an%20inclusive%20and%20equitable%20strategy%2C%20where%20decisions%20around%20hiring%20and%20advancement%20are%20diversity-sensitive%2C%20delivering%20on%20the%20vision%20of%20equal%20opportunities%20for%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saundarya%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20West%2C%20DEI%20is%20meant%20to%20give%20a%20voice%20to%20the%20voiceless.%20It%20is%20also%20intended%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20views%20of%20the%20most%20junior%20employee%20are%20heard%20in%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20however%2C%20diversity%20is%20often%20viewed%20narrowly%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20%E2%80%98female%20hiring'%2C%20which%20means%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20opportunity%20to%20broaden%20the%20focus%20to%20policies%20that%20promote%20a%20truly%20inclusive%20workplace.%20Experts%20suggest%20that%20certain%20areas%20remain%20sacrosanct%2C%20where%20positive%20discrimination%20should%20have%20no%20place.%20Merit%20should%20always%20be%20the%20sole%20criterion%20for%20selection%2C%20as%20the%20impact%20of%20an%20incorrect%20decision%2C%20whether%20by%20omission%20or%20commission%2C%20could%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNever%20give%20away%20board%20positions%2C%20management%20roles%2C%20promotions%2C%20and%20hire%20%E2%80%98only%20diversity%20candidates'.%20This%20does%20more%20harm%20to%20the%20cause%20than%20good.%20Inclusion%20must%20always%20feel%20inclusive.%20If%20you%20remain%20true%20to%20the%20principles%20of%20meritocracy%2C%20you%20will%20eliminate%20any%20bias%20against%20diversity%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmericans%20have%20displayed%20their%20resistance%20to%20this%20form%20of%20affirmative%20action%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%20rejection%20of%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20a%20Black%20and%20South%20Asian%20woman%2C%20who%20critics%20labelled%20a%20%26quot%3BDEI%20hire%26quot%3B.%20Let's%20hope%20that%20India's%20approach%20to%20DEI%20avoids%20the%20pitfalls%20of%20unconscious%20bias.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731310380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fi371ppl8_hiring_625x300_11_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmusk-to-ackman-the-growing-opposition-to-inclusive-hiring-6991985%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20whole%20concept%20of%20DEI%20which%20encompasses%20women%2C%20people%20of%20colour%2C%20and%20those%20in%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%20has%20come%20under%20attack%20in%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20Trump%20and%20Putin's%20first%20phone%20call%20since%20the%20election%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20al