0Sunday%2C%20invoking%20nostalgia%20among%20crew%20and%20members%20a%20day%20before%20the%20carrier's%20time%20in%20the%20Indian%20aviation%20landscape%20was%20to%20come%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20full-service%20carrier%20Vistara%2C%20which%20is%20a%2051%3A49%20per%20cent%20joint%20venture%20between%20Tata%20Sons%20and%20Singapore%20Airlines%2C%20is%20all%20set%20to%20merge%20with%20Air%20India%20on%20November%2012.%20In%20an%20Instagram%20post%2C%20the%20airline%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20plane%20ascends%2C%20so%20do%20our%20dreams%3B%20let's%20glide%20toward%20the%20future%2C%20where%20the%20sky%20isn't%20the%20limit%2C%20but%20just%20the%20beginning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Is%20Vistara%20Merging%20With%20Air%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingapore's%20flagship%20carrier%20announced%20a%20plan%20to%20merge%20the%20decade-old%20Vistara%20and%20Tata-owned%20Air%20India%20in%20November%202022%2C%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20create%20a%20dominant%20full-service%20airline%20in%20the%20domestic%20and%20international%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20merger%20process%2C%20however%2C%20was%20anything%20but%20smooth%2C%20with%20problems%20like%20pilot%20shortages%20causing%20widespread%20flight%20cancellations%20and%20Vistara%20crew%20protesting%20over%20plans%20to%20align%20their%20salary%20structures%20with%20Air%20India%20proving%20to%20be%20hurdles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20merger%20concludes%20on%20Monday%2C%20Vistara's%2049%20per%20cent%20owner%20Singapore%20Airlines%20will%20have%20a%2025.1%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20Air%20India.%20Singapore%20Airlines%20will%20make%20an%20additional%20investment%20of%20Rs%203%2C194.5%20crore%20in%20Tata%20Group-owned%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Is%20Air%20India%20Orchestrating%20The%20Transition%20For%20Fliers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India%20has%20deployed%20additional%20resources%2C%20including%20help%20desk%20kiosks%2C%20at%20touch%20points%20and%20airports%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20experience%20for%20Vistara%20passengers.%20There%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bcustomer%20support%20staff%20wearing%20'How%20may%20I%20assist%20you%3F'%20Air%20India%20x%20Vistara%20branded%20t-shirts%20for%20support%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20will%20work%20with%20airport%20security%20to%20guide%20customers%20with%20old%20Vistara%20tickets%20to%20the%20nearest%20help%20desk%20or%20to%20Air%20India%20customer%20support%20staff%20and%20deploy%20advisory%20on%20self-service%20kiosks.%20In%20due%20course%2C%20Vistara%20airport%20ticketing%20offices%20and%20check-in%20terminals%20will%20become%20that%20of%20Air%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVistara%20aircraft%20will%20be%20identified%20by%20a%20special%20four-digit%20Air%20India%20code%20beginning%20with%20the%20digit%20'2'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%202%2C70%2C000%20customers%20who%20had%20booked%20Vistara%20flights%20have%20been%20migrated%20to%20Air%20India%2C%20and%20more%20than%204.5%20million%20Vistara%20loyalty%20programme%20members%20are%20being%20migrated%20to%20Air%20India's%20loyalty%20programme.%20Further%2C%20customers%20calling%20the%20Vistara%20contact%20centre%20will%20be%20automatically%20directed%20to%20Air%20India%20representatives%2C%20who%20will%20ensure%20a%20seamless%20experience%20during%20this%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20integrated%20entity%20will%20have%20a%20fleet%20of%20more%20than%20200%20planes%2C%20offering%20connectivity%20to%2090%20domestic%20and%20international%20destinations.%20Air%20India's%20narrowbody%20fleet%20continues%20to%20be%20upgraded%20with%20new%20aircraft%20being%20delivered%2C%20legacy%20aircraft%20being%20refitted%20with%20entirely%20new%20interiors%20and%20Vistara's%20catering%20now%20also%20extended%20to%20Air%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India's%20widebody%20fleet%20has%20also%20been%20augmented%20with%20the%20entry%20of%20six%20A350%20aircraft%20that%20have%20started%20to%20fly%20between%20Delhi%20and%20London%2C%20and%20Delhi%20and%20New%20York%2C%20the%20airline%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20month%20after%20the%20merger%2C%20nearly%201%2C15%2C000%20passengers%20who%20had%20purchased%20Vistara%20tickets%20pre-merger%20are%20expected%20to%20fly%20on%20unified%20Air%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Managerial%20Reshuffle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVistara%20chief%20executive%20officer%20Vinod%20Kanan%2C%20who%20has%20also%20been%20holding%20the%20role%20of%20Chief%20Integration%20Officer%20for%20the%20merger%20of%20the%20two%20entities%2C%20will%20continue%20in%20the%20latter%20role%20post-merger.%20Besides%2C%20he%20will%20be%20a%20member%20of%20the%20management%20committee%20and%20report%20directly%20to%20Air%20India%20CEO%20Campbell%20Wilson%2C%20a%20company%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepak%20Rajawat%2C%20Chief%20Commercial%20Officer%20of%20Vistara%20will%20take%20up%20the%20position%20of%20Chief%20Financial%20Officer%20at%20the%20low-cost%20arm%20Air%20India%20Express%2C%20reporting%20to%20its%20chief%20executive%20officer%20Aloke%20Singh%20and%20also%20support%20Air%20India%20Group%20CFO%20Sanjay%20Sharma%20in%20strategic%20initiatives%20and%20projects.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Vikas%20Agarwal%2C%20the%20current%20CFO%20of%20Air%20India%20Express%2C%20will%20move%20to%20a%20new%20role%20in%20Air%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20vice%20president%20for%20flight%20operations%20at%20Vistara%20Hamish%20Maxwell%20has%20assumed%20an%20advisory%20role%20to%20Air%20India%20Express%20CEO%20Aloke%20Singh%20while%20Pushpinder%20Singh%2C%20Chief%20Operations%20Officer%20of%20Air%20India%20Express%2C%20returns%20to%20flying%2C%20as%20per%20the%20statement.%20A%20successor%20for%20Singh%20will%20be%20announced%20in%20due%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepa%20Chadha%20and%20Vinod%20Bhatt%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20HR%20%26amp%3B%20Corporate%20Affairs%20and%20Chief%20Information%20Officer%20of%20Vistara%20respectively%2C%20will%20take%20on%20senior%20roles%20at%20other%20Tata%20group%20companies%2C%20the%20statement%20said%20adding%20that%20Vistara%20CFO%20Niyant%20Maru%2C%20who%20had%20continued%20beyond%20his%20superannuation%20date%20to%20see%20through%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20merger%2C%20will%20retire%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20current%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20other%20Air%20India%20Group%20CXO%20roles%20and%20reporting%20lines%20roles%20will%20remain%20unchanged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Are%20Air%20India%20Pilots%20Miffed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20of%20Air%20India%20pilots%20is%20unhappy%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Vistara%20merger%20over%20different%20retirement%20age%20limits%20for%20pilots%20of%20the%20two%20Tata%20Group-owned%20airlines%20as%20the%20management%20is%20yet%20to%20address%20the%20issue%2C%20sources%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Air%20India%2C%20the%20retirement%20age%20for%20pilots%20and%20other%20staff%20is%2058%20years%2C%20whereas%20at%20Vistara%20it%20is%2060%20years.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20management%20was%20prompt%20in%20bringing%20parity%20in%20terms%20of%20salary%20structure%20and%20other%20working%20conditions%20of%20the%20employees%20of%20the%20two%20airlines%20as%20part%20of%20the%20merger%20process%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20two%20different%20retirement%20age%20limits%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20said%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAir%20India%20Only%20Full-Service%20Carrier%20In%20Country%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVistara%2C%20like%20many%20other%20airlines%2C%20entered%20Indian%20aviation%20after%20the%20liberalisation%20of%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20norms.%20In%202012%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20UPA%20government%20allowed%20foreign%20airlines%20to%20buy%20up%20to%2049%20per%20cent%20in%20a%20domestic%20carrier%2C%20which%20later%20resulted%20in%20the%20now%20defunct%20Jet%20Airways%20securing%2024%20per%20cent%20stake%20from%20Gulf%20carrier%20Etihad%20besides%20the%20birth%20of%20AirAsia%20India%20and%20Vistara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20operations%20commencing%20on%20started%20flying%20on%20January%209%2C%202015%2C%20Vistara%20soon%20became%20synonymous%20with%20quality%20food%20and%20service%20and%20cultivated%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Kingfisher%20went%20belly%20up%20in%202012%20while%20Air%20Sahara%2C%20which%20was%20acquired%20by%20Jet%20Airways%20and%20renamed%20as%20JetLite%2C%20sank%20with%20Jet%20Airways%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVistara's%20winding%20up%20will%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20full-service%20carriers%20just%20one%20from%20five%20in%20a%20span%20of%20over%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENostalgic%20Fliers%20Bid%20Goodbye%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20was%20flooded%20with%20posts%20from%20loyal%20Vistara%20fliers%2C%20who%20remembered%20the%20airline%20for%20delivering%20the%20%26quot%3Bnew%20feeling%26quot%3B%20in%20travel.%20Many%20posted%20pictures%20from%20their%20travels%20on%20board%20the%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20crew%20was%20nostalgic%20during%20in-flight%20announcements%20and%20in%20true%20Vistara%20fashion%20played%20Kal%20Ho%20Na%20Ho%20upon%20landing!%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20brand%20deserves%20to%20live%20on%20through%20case%20studies%20and%20employee%20accounts.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(h%2Ft%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheSanjivKapoor%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40TheSanjivKapoor%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20sharing%20insights%20from%20his%20time%20at%20Vistara%20and%20Jet)%203%2F4%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Anubhav%20Goyal%20(%40anubhavgo)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fanubhavgo%2Fstatus%2F1855579362264785065%3Fref_src%3Dtwsr