0about%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20multiple%20surgical%20procedures%20and%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20cosmetic%20enhancements%20in%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fpeople-culture%2Ftrending-china%2Farticle%2F3285791%2Fchina-woman-dies-after-6-cosmetic-surgeries-day-family-get-half-us168000-requested%3Fmodule%3Dtop_story%26pgtype%3Dsection%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20woman%20who%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Liu%2C%20belonging%20to%20a%20rural%20area%20in%20Guigang%2C%20Guangxi%20province%2C%20southern%20China%20visited%20a%20clinic%20in%20Nanning%20on%20December%209%2C%202020.%C2%A0She%20also%20took%20out%20a%20loan%20of%20over%2040%2C000%20yuan%20(US%245%2C600)%20to%20finance%20the%20procedures.%C2%A0Liu%20first%20underwent%20double%20eyelid%20surgery%20and%20a%20nose%20job%2C%20which%20lasted%20five%20hours%2C%20followed%20by%20liposuction%20on%20her%20thighs%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extracted%20fat%20was%20then%20injected%20into%20her%20face%20and%20breasts%20in%20another%20five-hour%20procedure.%20However%2C%20just%20as%20Liu%20was%20discharged%20on%20December%2011%2C%20she%20suddenly%20collapsed%20in%20the%20clinic's%20lift.%C2%A0Despite%20emergency%20efforts%20by%20the%20clinic%20staff%2C%20Liu's%20condition%20deteriorated%20rapidly.%20She%20was%20rushed%20to%20The%20Second%20Nanning%20People's%20Hospital%2C%20where%20she%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20later%20that%20afternoon.%20The%20autopsy%20report%20showed%20that%20she%20died%20from%20''acute%20respiratory%20failure%20due%20to%20pulmonary%20embolism%20after%20liposuction''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%2C%20Liu's%20family%20took%20legal%20action%2C%20filing%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20the%20clinic%20at%20Jiangnan%20District%20People's%20Court%20of%20Nanning%20City.%20They%20demanded%20co