2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esays%20that's%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabortion-pill-women-stockpile-mifepristone-trump-presidency-experts-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20are%20stockpiling%20reproductive%20healthcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20products%20now%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20headed%20back%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWisp%2C%20which%20serves%20over%201.2%20million%20patients%20nationwide%2C%20reported%20a%201%2C000%25%20increase%20in%20emergency%20contraception%20purchases%20from%20November%205%20to%20November%206.%20Wisp%20CEO%20Monica%20Cepak%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20women%20are%20%26quot%3Btaking%20action%20as%20they%20navigate%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20these%20next%20few%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20data%20indicates%20to%20us%20that%20women%20are%20really%20scared%20and%20are%20using%20this%20moment%20in%20time%20to%20take%20back%20agency%20over%20their%20reproductive%20rights%20by%20stockpiling%20things%20like%20emergency%20contraception%20and%20investing%20in%20preventive%20reproductive%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20Cepak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20first%20term%2C%20Trump%20put%20three%20conservative%20justices%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-abortion-decision-final-ruling-scotus-roe-v-wade-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoverturned%20Roe%20v.%20Wade%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20decision%20undid%20nationwide%20abortion%20protections%20and%20allowed%2013%20states%20to%20pass%20laws%20that%20effectively%20banned%20abortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Trump%20took%20credit%20for%20ending%20the%20decadeslong%20precedent%20of%20legalized%20abortion%20nationwide.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20it%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-abortion-roe-v-wade-supreme-court-gop-primary-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI'm%20proud%20to%20have%20done%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20else%20was%20going%20to%20get%20that%20done%20but%20me%2C%20and%20we%20did%20it%2C%20and%20we%20did%20something%20that%20was%20a%20miracle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2024%20hours%20after%20Election%20Day%2C%20Wisp%20said%20it%20saw%20a%201%2C650%25%20increase%20in%20new%20patients%20purchasing%20emergency%20contraception.%20There%20was%20a%20600%25%20increase%20in%20medication%20abortion%20sales%20and%20a%2050%25%20increase%20in%20birth%20control%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Wisp's%20reproductive%20health%20sales%20(of%20emergency%20contraception%2C%20birth%20control%2C%20and%20medication%20abortion%20products)%20doubled%20compared%20to%20the%20week%20prior%20to%20the%20election%2C%20the%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20that%20momentum%20to%20sustain%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%20and%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Cepak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20purchases%20came%20from%20women%20in%20both%20anti-abortion%20states%20as%20well%20as%20states%20with%20widespread%20access%20to%20reproductive%20healthcare.%20Emergency%20contraception%20purchases%20surged%20in%20Texas%2C%20Indiana%2C%20and%20Oklahoma%2C%20where%20there%20are%20strict%20restrictions%2C%20but%20sales%20also%20increased%20in%20states%20like%20California%20and%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20being%20states%20where%20reproductive%20rights%20are%20fully%20protected%2C%20we're%20seeing%20women%20take%20precautionary%20measures%20as%20the%20future%20remains%20uncertain%2C%26quot%3B%20Wisp%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmy%20Hagstrom%20Miller%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Whole%20Woman's%20Health%2C%20which%20operates%20abortion%20clinics%20in%20multiple%20states%2C%20said%20her%20organization%20is%20also%20seeing%20a%20surge%20in%20demand%20for%20contraceptive%20and%20abortion%20medication.%3