20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20we%20told%20people%20about%20our%20work%20with%20The%20Batti%20Project%20in%20Arunachal%20and%20mentioned%20that%20we%20might%20need%20support.%20Instead%20of%20asking%20for%20donations%2C%20we%20encouraged%20them%20to%20contribute%20by%20donating%20their%20electronic%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20time%2C%20Ittisha%20had%20chosen%20e-waste%20as%20the%20subject%20for%20her%20dissertation.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20many%20people%20were%20researching%20electronic%20waste%20at%20that%20time.%20So%20I%20would%20read%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20papers%20and%20then%20try%20to%20identify%20places%20where%20electronic%20waste%20recycling%20is%20happening%20in%20and%20around%20Delhi.%20Then%20I%20would%20go%20out%20onto%20the%20field%20to%20locate%20the%20places%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20exposing%20her%20to%20e-waste%2C%20her%20on-ground%20work%20during%20her%20thesis%20also%20exposed%20her%20to%20solid%20waste%20and%20the%20many%20problems%20it%20brings%20along%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20per%20a%202021%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocuments1.worldbank.org%2Fcurated%2Fen%2F823241618991659221%2Fpdf%2FIndia-Sustainable-Solid-Waste-Management-in-Mountain-Areas.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Bank%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20waste%20generation%20in%20India%20is%20projected%20to%20reach%20388.77%20million%20tonnes%20a%20year%20by%202030.%20The%20ecologically%20sensitive%20Indian%20Himalayan%20Region%20(IHR)%20that%20stretches%20from%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20West%20to%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20East%20is%20particularly%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20challenges%20this%20may%20bring.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20reveals%20that%20municipal%20solid%20waste%20generation%20in%20IHR%20is%20approximately%2014%2C450%20tonnes%20per%20day%20or%20over%205.2%20million%20tonnes%20per%20year.%20A%20majority%20of%20this%20problem%20plagues%20urban%20centres%2C%20but%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20tourism%20and%20development%20to%20cater%20to%20it%2C%20this%20number%20is%20expected%20to%20rise%20exponentially%20in%20the%20next%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20after%20completing%20her%20dissertation%2C%20Ittisha%20decided%20to%20start%20something%20to%20address%20this%20problem%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20states.%20She%20partnered%20with%20Merwyn%20and%20Rajiv%2C%20initially%20working%20for%20The%20Batti%20Project%2C%20and%20soon%20establishing%20the%20Northeast%20Waste%20Collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProject%20Sangti%3A%20A%20community%20takes%20charge%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20journey%20to%20Sangti%20began%20in%202018%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ittisha%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CA%20friend%20who%20runs%20a%20travel%20company%2C%20which%20was%20just%20starting%20out%20at%20the%20time%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20ask%20for%20my%20help.%E2%80%9D%20She%20was%20given%20the%20role%20of%20tour%20instructor%2C%20leading%20a%20group%20of%20school%20students%20to%20a%20summer%20camp.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20something%20about%20this%20place%20%E2%80%94%20it%20felt%20like%20%3Cem%3Edeja%20vu%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20river%2C