0they%20have%20established%2035%20dialysis%20centres%20in%20seven%20states%20across%20North%20India%2C%20providing%20over%2015%2C000%20sessions%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20idea%20was%20very%20clear%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20vision%20comes%20to%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20really%20united%20the%20three%20founders%20was%20their%20shared%20background%20from%20Tier%202%20cities.%20Prabhat%2C%20a%20lawyer%20from%20Jabalpur.%20Dr%20Saurabh%20from%20Dehradun%20with%2018%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20and%20Pankaj%20from%20Agra%2C%20a%20corporate%20finance%20expert%2C%20all%20recognised%20the%20pressing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333216%2Fiit-guwahati-invents-sensor-for-diabetes-diet-low-glycemic-index-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneed%20for%20better%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20moving%20his%20parents%20to%20Gurgaon%20in%202015%2C%20Prabhat%20started%20brainstorming%20possible%20solutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoving%20my%20parents%20out%20of%20their%20comfort%20zone%20was%20not%20easy.%20I%20was%20shocked%20that%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20quality%20dialysis%20centres%20in%20Jabalpur%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20small%20city.%20I%20found%20people%20travelling%20100%20km%20daily%20for%20dialysis%2C%20and%20it%20was%20heartbreaking.%20While%20I%20could%20relocate%20my%20father%2C%20not%20everyone%20has%20that%20luxury%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Prabhat%2C%20CEO%20of%20VitusCare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22